5.2 Agent processing (derived intelligence)
After ingestion (or on a schedule), backend agent modules process snapshot data:

Step	Agent	Input tables	Output tables
Schedule confidence	Delivery Performance	throughput_snapshots, milestones, projects	delivery_confidence_scores, milestones.status
Risk detection	Delivery Performance	throughput_snapshots, delivery_confidence_scores	risk_alerts, bottlenecks
Quality drift	Quality Intelligence	quality_snapshots (trend)	quality_snapshots.has_drift_alert, risk_alerts (type quality_drift)
