10. Error Handling and Exception Paths
The following paths are specified in project documentation. Implementation details (HTTP status codes, retry policies) belong in 09. API Specification.md once defined.

10.1 Authentication and authorisation failures
Condition	Expected behaviour
Missing or expired JWT	Frontend redirects to login; API returns 401
Valid JWT but wrong role for action	API returns 403; no data leakage in error body
Cross-tenant access attempt	PostgreSQL RLS returns zero rows or INSERT rejection; log as security event
Client attempts to INSERT communication draft	RLS denies; only service_role creates drafts
10.2 Agent and LLM failures
Condition	Expected behaviour
LLM provider timeout or error	Do not persist partial agent_queries; return user-visible error; no uncited answer
Retrieval returns no evidence	Agent must not fabricate project status (01. Project Summary.md — Client Interaction governance)
Evidence link insert fails	Roll back agent query transaction; do not expose answer without citations
10.3 Data validation failures
Condition	Expected behaviour
Ingestion row violates CHECK constraints	Reject row; log validation error; do not partial-insert snapshot batch
Duplicate snapshot date for project	throughput_snapshots UNIQUE constraint rejects; surface to ingestion operator
DM rejects communication	status = 'rejected'; draft retained for audit; regeneration required before resubmit
10.4 Notification delivery failures
Condition	Expected behaviour
Email provider failure	notifications.sent_at remains NULL; retry queue (implementation TBD); in-app notification still created
10.5 Environment and data governance
Condition	Expected behaviour
Non-prod environment	Seed data only from supabase/seed/ — never live client production data
Prod promotion blocked	Requires client approval, governance sign-off, security validation, compliance review (01. Project Summary.md §6)
11. Audit and Evidence Trail
Every AI-generated artefact must be traceable:

Artefact	Primary table	Evidence table	Immutability
NL query answer	agent_queries	agent_query_evidence_links	Append-only
Client communication	client_communications	communication_evidence_links	Draft mutable until sent; links immutable
Risk alert narrative	risk_alerts.detail	Inline JSONB contributing_causes + optional evidence links	Soft-delete only
Delivery confidence	delivery_confidence_scores	Derived from cited snapshots	Append-only time series
Frontend must render evidence citations as navigable links to the underlying metric or snapshot (01. Project Summary.md §3 item 13).

